209
00:10:40.006 --> 00:10:41.736
We ran the prints but
the system was down.

210
00:10:41.841 --> 00:10:43.152
By the time we got a
match he was gone.

211
00:10:43.176 --> 00:10:44.816
He said his flight
was leaving in an hour.

212
00:10:44.844 --> 00:10:47.040
So you let him walk? Great.

213
00:10:47.147 --> 00:10:49.013
We thought we had a
50-year-old cross dresser

214
00:10:49.115 --> 00:10:51.880
